what doesn t bigfix do stanford answers stanford university stanford answers what doesn t bigfix do categories accounts and ids administrative applications anti virus and security computer operating systems connecting to the network desktop hardware and support email and calendar help desk restricted information on it services software at stanford stanford hospital and clinics telephones and cable tv unix systems and software web services user login login with your sunet id home what doesn t bigfix do search this site there is no single complete solution for problems of computer security bigfix will help to ensure that operating systems are securely patched other good security practices are still essential such practices include having a minimum number of user accounts on your computer choosing strong passwords protecting passwords from theft using up to date and properly configured antivirus software using a firewall when possible configuring file sharing properly and securely if you need to share files shutting down your computer when it's not in use not double clicking suspicious e mail attachments correctly configuring operating system security settings and disabling unnecessary services installing bigfix helps keep your computer and the network safe by reducing the risk of attacks like ms blaster bigfix doesn t mean that you re safe it means that you re safer for more information about how to secure your computer please see the secure computing web site bigfix stanford university 450 serra mall stanford california 94305 650 723 2300 terms of use copyright complaints
